        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/money-monster.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/money-monster.html",
            "title": "Money Monster",
            "summary": "Time has not been kind to my original black and white drawing.",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/20251106_051321.jpg\" data-size=\"3024x4032\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/20251106_051321-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/ComfyUI_00619_.png\" data-size=\"1240x1656\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/ComfyUI_00619_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1026\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/ComfyUI_00617_.png\" data-size=\"1240x1656\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/ComfyUI_00617_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1026\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/ComfyUI_00616_.png\" data-size=\"1240x1656\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/ComfyUI_00616_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1026\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>Time has not been kind to my original black and white drawing. I will have to try a full restoration using AI. I did use AI for the section that was okay. I gave it minimal guidance to what to create because i wanted to see how it interpreted the design. As you can see from the results it got the idea I was trying to convey with my design.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/ComfyUI_00617_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-06T00:35:59-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-06T00:35:59-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/drawing-my-friends.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/drawing-my-friends.html",
            "title": "Drawing my Friends",
            "summary": "This is a fun black and white sketch surreal style. I used&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/26/gallery/ComfyUI_00454_.png\" data-size=\"1224x1688\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/26/gallery/ComfyUI_00454_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1059\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/26/gallery/scan0023.jpg\" data-size=\"1601x2091\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/26/gallery/scan0023-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1003\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This is a fun black and white sketch surreal style. I used AI testing how it would interpret the shapes, people and creatures in the sketch. I gave it minimal guidance to see what is thought it was seeing. I find AI fun and intriguing because it adds a step to the creative process, in the past when I got stuck on a piece of design, I would have to wait till inspiration hit, now AI as a tool can speed up this process.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/26/ComfyUI_00454_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Rough Sketch",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-06T00:18:32-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-06T00:18:32-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/man-with-fish-bowl.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/man-with-fish-bowl.html",
            "title": "Man with Fish Bowl",
            "summary": "This is black and white sketch that is one part of a&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/25/gallery/ComfyUI_00455_.png\" data-size=\"1224x1688\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/25/gallery/ComfyUI_00455_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1059\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/25/gallery/scan0015.jpg\" data-size=\"1590x2086\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/25/gallery/scan0015-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1008\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/25/gallery/rave-world-lg.jpg\" data-size=\"770x367\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/25/gallery/rave-world-lg-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"366\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This is black and white sketch that is one part of a large fine art painting I made. This is a surreal piece that I gave to AI to see what it could do with a surreal image. this AI image had its own colorful interpretation of the shapes and how they related. i have included the fine art painting that this sketch was part of.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/25/ComfyUI_00455_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Fine Art Painting",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-05T23:12:38-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-05T23:14:18-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/friends-forever.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/friends-forever.html",
            "title": "Friends Forever",
            "summary": "This is a not the best version of this drawing I made&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/ComfyUI_00438_.png\" data-size=\"1768x1168\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/ComfyUI_00438_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"507\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/ComfyUI_00436_.png\" data-size=\"1768x1168\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/ComfyUI_00436_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"507\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/ComfyUI_00434_.png\" data-size=\"1768x1168\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/ComfyUI_00434_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"507\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/girl-with-dog-lg.jpg\" data-size=\"598x396\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/girl-with-dog-lg-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"598\" height=\"396\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This is a not the best version of this drawing I made a long time ago, the digital copy has a lot of extra noise, but you can see my style, I added a touch of whimsy to the picture I drew this portrait of a friend and her dog. The color versions are the AI versions I made while seeing how much additional whimsy I could add while maintaining the original black and white drawing style. I also experimented with extending the original image by making the size of the AI image larger then the input.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/ComfyUI_00434_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-05T22:44:58-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-05T23:01:20-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/blur-the-line.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/blur-the-line.html",
            "title": "Blur the Line",
            "summary": "This is a print advertisement for a unique clothing material. This image&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/23/gallery/skater_l.jpg\" data-size=\"333x500\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/23/gallery/skater_l-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/23/gallery/ComfyUI_00562_.png\" data-size=\"1240x1656\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/23/gallery/ComfyUI_00562_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1026\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/23/gallery/ComfyUI_00558_.png\" data-size=\"1240x1656\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/23/gallery/ComfyUI_00558_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1026\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/23/gallery/ComfyUI_00541_.png\" data-size=\"1240x1656\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/23/gallery/ComfyUI_00541_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1026\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This is a print advertisement for a unique clothing material. This image was fabricated in Photoshop. I used this for an AI image input to test AI ability to use the general composition of the image and the likeness of the skater while removing the text and adding new elements. </p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/23/ComfyUI_00558_.png",
